OL,3,CAmir Khan warns wedding planners
OL,4,Cagainst using his venue over rent feud
OL,6,FFormer World Champion boxer Amir Khan
OL,7,Fhas warned people not to book weddings
OL,8,Fat his venue following a rent dispute
OL,9,Fwith the current operator.
OL,11,FPosting a statement on X, Khan said he
OL,12,Fwas pursuing legal action against
OL,13,FExcellency Midlands, who run The
OL,14,FBalmayna in Bolton, and claimed they
OL,15,Fhad not paid rent in close to three
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FBut the events company labelled these
OL,19,Fclaims "baseless", calling his
OL,20,Fcomments "malicious" and "defamatory".
