OL,3,CAmir Khan warns wedding planners
OL,4,Cagainst using his venue over rent feud
OL,6,FExcellency Midlands went on to
OL,7,Freassure clients that the venue
OL,8,Fremains fully operational and all
OL,9,Fbookings would go ahead as planned.
OL,11,FIn his statement, Khan said: "Please
OL,12,Fbe informed that Mohammed from
OL,13,FExcellency has NOT made any rental
OL,14,Fpayments for almost three years
OL,15,Ffollowing the initial 18-month rent-
OL,16,Ffree period.
OL,18,F"We advise anyone who has booked the
OL,19,Fwedding to hold off until this issue
OL,20,Fis resolved, as I would not want you
OL,21,Fto risk losing your money or deposits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
