OL,3,CAmir Khan warns wedding planners
OL,4,Cagainst using his venue over rent feud
OL,6,F"We recognise that many individuals
OL,7,Fhave made reservations at the venue,
OL,8,Fand I regret to inform you that I am
OL,9,Ftaking legal action regarding this
OL,10,Fsituation."
OL,12,FIn response, Midlands Excellency
OL,13,Fposted a statement on The Balmayna's
OL,14,FInstagram, in which they claimed the
OL,15,Fdispute was a "private landlord-tenant
OL,16,Fissue".
OL,18,FIt said: "To be absolutely clear, Amir
OL,19,FKhan has no involvement whatsoever in
OL,20,Fthe ownership, management, or
OL,21,Foperation of Balmayna.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
