OL,6,F"The matter being referred to publicly
OL,7,Frelates solely to a private landlord-
OL,8,Ftenant issue, which is being addressed
OL,9,Fthrough the appropriate legal and
OL,10,Fprofessional channels.
OL,12,F"Certain recent comments circulating
OL,13,Fonline are misinformed, baseless, and
OL,14,Fshould be disregarded. Alhamdulillah,
OL,15,Frather than being affected by such
OL,16,Fcommentary, the Balmayna Group
OL,17,Fcontinues to grow stronger, more
OL,18,Fstable, and more successful.
