OL,3,CAmir Khan warns wedding planners
OL,4,Cagainst using his venue over rent feud
OL,6,F"We do not allow malicious or
OL,7,Fdefamatory remarks to distract us from
OL,8,Four responsibilities, and we will not
OL,9,Fengage in public disputes or online
OL,10,Fspeculation. We believe firmly in
OL,11,Fhandling matters lawfully,
OL,12,Fprofessionally, and privately.
OL,14,F"We would like to reassure all clients
OL,15,Fthat there is absolutely no impact on
OL,16,Fconfirmed bookings, events, or
OL,17,Fdeposits. Balmayna remains fully
OL,18,Foperational, financially secure, and
OL,19,Fcommitted to delivering the
OL,20,Fexceptionally high standards for which
OL,21,Fwe are known.
